snippet.title: Mini Book Haul, Bookish Candles & Reorganising My Shelves (Chill Weekend Reading Vlog)
snippet.description:
A bit of an impromptu reading vlog, with a few book-related goodies sprinkled in~

The book I'm reading in this vlog is The Spider by Leo Carew

The candles are from Grace & Honey, and the sprayed books are from InkyFoxBooks
